PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of RUTH A. SPENCE, of Yellowknife, Northwest Territories, as a member of the National Capital Commission to hold office during pleasure for a term of one year, in the place of Darlene Mandeville, whose term has expired.
